<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7794&amp;p=33555#p33555"><![CDATA[
Hi,<br /><br />when I was using windows 10 1511 I had no pb with classic shell<br />I'm now using windows 10 1607 (for 2 weeks) and every time I close my computer I have a window with an error and in the events administration I found informations about this error :<br /><blockquote class="editor"><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline">- &lt;Event xmlns=&quot;http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events/event&quot;&gt;</span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline">- &lt;System&gt;</span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;Provider Name=&quot;.NET Runtime&quot; /&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;EventID Qualifiers=&quot;0&quot;&gt;1026&lt;/EventID&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;Level&gt;2&lt;/Level&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;Task&gt;0&lt;/Task&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;Keywords&gt;0x80000000000000&lt;/Keywords&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;TimeCreated SystemTime=&quot;2017-07-31T23:02:56.096986400Z&quot; /&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;EventRecordID&gt;4696&lt;/EventRecordID&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;Channel&gt;Application&lt;/Channel&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;Computer&gt;PC-DE-FRED&lt;/Computer&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;Security /&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;/System&gt;</span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline">- &lt;EventData&gt;</span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;Data&gt;Application : explorer.exe Version du Framework : v4.0.30319 Description : le processus a été arrêté en raison d'une exception non gérée. Informations sur l'exception : code d'exception c0000005, adresse d'exception 00007FF77AA08A22&lt;/Data&gt; </span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;/EventData&gt;</span></span></blockquote><blockquote class="editor"><span style="color:#0000ee;"><span style="text-decoration: underline"> &lt;/Event&gt;</span></span></blockquote></blockquote><br /><br />If, before to stop windows, i right click on the start button and quit classic shell, I have no error window and no error in the events administration ! Error is only with your application !<br /><br />When I arrived on this forum to try to find a solution and saw so many bugs for your 'stable' version, a more than one year version, I understood that this application was dangerous for my computer and only a bad joke so I uninstalled it !<br /><br />Do the same, guys !<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=14336">Mahab</a> — Wed Aug 02, 2017 1:50 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
